params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The name of the agent to update or create entity types in. Format: projects/<Project ID>/agent.

params.name: data.entity_type_batch_uri
params.description: The URI to a Google Cloud Storage file containing entity types to update or create. The file format can either be a serialized proto (of EntityBatch type) or a JSON object. Note: The URI must start with "gs://".

params.name: data.entity_type_batch_inline
params.description: The collection of entity types to update or create.

params.name: data.language_code
params.description: Optional. The language of entity synonyms defined in entity_types. If not specified, the agent's default language is used. Many languages are supported. Note: languages must be enabled in the agent before they can be used.

params.name: data.update_mask
params.description: Optional. The mask to control which fields get updated.
